In this section we will describe the minimum styling required on your website or application to meet Oxfordshire County Council standards. 

If you are not able to meet the minimum requirements, or for any other question related to styling please contact email[@]hehe

Your application should meet the Digital service standard and you will also need to follow our style guide for the:

- typography
- header
- footer
- colour scheme